snippet.title: Warhammer 40,000: Dakka Squadron - Flyboyz Edition Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Warhammer 40,000: Dakka Squadron - Flyboyz Edition. Blazing, Ork aerial combat waged across 41st millennium battlefields. Dakka Squadron is a fast-paced, aerial shooter where you are an Ork Flyboy, taking to the skies to do what Orks do best - fight!


Available February 18th, 2020!


Wishlist on Steam (and try the demo): 
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1253190/Warhammer_40000_Dakka_Squadron__Flyboyz_Edition/
